OL,3,CBurnham says he will 'pause' the early
OL,4,Crelease scheme for prisoners
OL,6,FThe prime minister has said he will
OL,7,F"put a pause" on the early release
OL,8,Fscheme for prisoners, which was due to
OL,9,Fstart in September.
OL,11,FUnder the new Sentencing Act set to
OL,12,Fcome into force in September, some
OL,13,F6,000 criminals were due to be
OL,14,Freleased under the early prison
OL,15,Frelease scheme.
OL,17,FAndy Burnham said: "Keeping the public
OL,18,Fsafe will always be my top priority.
OL,26,@yD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
