OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784854087
OL,3,CBurnham says he will 'pause' the early
OL,4,Crelease scheme for prisoners
OL,6,F"I am working closely with the new
OL,7,FJustice Secretary and have instructed
OL,8,Fmy team to put a pause on the changes
OL,9,Fthat were due to start in September."
OL,11,FThis follows concerns raised by the
OL,12,Fmother of PC Harper, who said that the
OL,13,Ffact two of her son's killers are
OL,14,Fbeing considered for early release is
OL,15,F"another letdown".
OL,17,FLissie Harper, his widow, described
OL,18,Fthe scheme as "deplorable".
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@OOUzD@ZO]
