OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784854087
OL,3,CBurnham says he will 'pause' the early
OL,4,Crelease scheme for prisoners
OL,6,FBurnham said: "No prisoners will be
OL,7,Flet out under this policy until we
OL,8,Fhave conducted an urgent review and
OL,9,Fdone everything we can to minimise
OL,10,Frisk to the public.
OL,12,F"Where changes are needed, we will not
OL,13,Fhesitate to make them."
OL,15,FPC Harper was 28 years old when he
OL,16,Fsustained fatal injuries while
OL,17,Fresponding to a quad bike theft in
OL,18,FSulhamstead, Berkshire, in August 2019.
OL,26,@nD@OOUtD@AOUuD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
