OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784854087
OL,3,CBurnham says he will 'pause' the early
OL,4,Crelease scheme for prisoners
OL,6,FThe driver of the vehicle which caused
OL,7,FPC Harper's death, Henry Long,
OL,8,Freceived a 16-year sentence, and was
OL,9,Fnot eligible for the scheme.
OL,11,FEarly release was a potential option
OL,12,Ffor Jessie Cole and Albert Bowers, who
OL,13,Fwere passengers in the car and handed
OL,14,F13 years in custody for manslaughter
OL,15,Fafter a trial at the Old Bailey in
OL,16,F2020.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
