OL,3,CBurnham says he will 'pause' the early
OL,4,Crelease scheme for prisoners
OL,6,FBoth men will now have to wait after
OL,7,Fthe prime minister has announced that
OL,8,Fno more prisoners will be released
OL,9,Funder the policy until a review is
OL,10,Fcomplete.
OL,12,FBurnham had previously said he would
OL,13,Freview the early release policy.
OL,15,FSpeaking to reporters on Wednesday he
OL,16,Fsaid: "I can't say that I can change
OL,17,Fthe policy completely, but I will look
OL,18,Fat it in detail before we go further
OL,19,Fforward".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
