OL,3,CBurnham says he will 'pause' the early
OL,4,Crelease scheme for prisoners
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FUnder the previous Conservative
OL,12,Fgovernments, only 500 additional
OL,13,Fprison places were created over 14
OL,14,Fyears and Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,15,Fgovernment faced issues with
OL,16,Fovercrowding in prisons.
OL,18,FThe early release scheme was designed
OL,19,Fto reduce this issue and ensure
OL,20,Fsuitable space for criminals who
OL,21,Freceive prison sentences.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
