OL,3,CBurnham says he will 'pause' the early
OL,4,Crelease scheme for prisoners
OL,6,FThe plan was introduced under former
OL,7,Fprisons officer Lord James Timpson who
OL,8,Fleft government on Monday following
OL,9,FStarmer's departure from No 10.
OL,11,FHe said it had been an "honour" to
OL,12,Fserve in the role and said he leaves
OL,13,F"our prisons and probation service in
OL,14,Fa much healthier and happier state
OL,15,Fthan two years ago".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
