OL,3,CBurnham says he will 'pause' the early
OL,4,Crelease scheme for prisoners
OL,6,FThere have been some suggestions that
OL,7,Fthe government could consider
OL,8,Freleasing non-violent women from
OL,9,Fprison instead of dangerous offenders
OL,10,Fand turning women's prisons into ones
OL,11,Ffor men.
OL,13,FConservative peer, Lord Garnier raised
OL,14,Fthe issue on Thursday and said: "There
OL,15,Fare 3,650 women in prison in England
OL,16,Fand Wales, and about 2,500 of those
OL,17,Fpeople ` that's to say, 70% of the
OL,18,Fwomen's prison population ` are in
OL,19,Fcustody for non-violent offences.
OL,26,@vD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
