CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1784854087
OL,3,CBurnham says he will 'pause' the early
OL,4,Crelease scheme for prisoners
OL,6,F"If the government thinks it's better
OL,7,Fto release violent criminals, child
OL,8,Fsex offenders, rather than that non-
OL,9,Fviolent cohort of women in prison, and
OL,10,Ffails to take the opportunity to free
OL,11,Fup prison places there, by re-rolling
OL,12,Fthose a woman's prison into a prison
OL,13,Ffor men, what the hell do they think
OL,14,Fthey're doing?"
